Let it be known:

At a threshold of 1x/wk Physical Therapy visit or 2x/wk Skilled Nursing visits, decreased the hospital readmission rates by 82% (for PT) and 48% (for SN) respectively!

Home Health is the most valuable, untapped resource in preventing hospital readmissions!! https://t.co/8PcID4sdik
